      "span_text": "The Seiberg -Witten curve, mentioned at the end of the previous paragraph, seems to be related to the CY through mirror symmetry: it was found that the mirror to a CY with a shrinking 4-cycle includes a Riemann surface which depends only on the local 4-cycle and not on the surrounding CY  ."
